{
  "name": "Magma Storm",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "type": "String",
      "label": "Description",
      "value": "<p>You ignite the ground and summon a devastating vortex of molten rock. Targets within the Area of Effect receive 2 @Condition[Ablaze] Conditions and suffer a <em>magic missile</em> hit with Damage +12.</p><p>This spell uses the @UUID[JournalEntry.CpVn7Hp5hz7NmpYu.JournalEntryPage.JcEoePfWMZkaFnJX#random-vortices]{Random Vortex}. On any round after the vortex moved 8 yards or less, it produces +1 smaller vortex for every +2 SL (maximum 3). These smaller vortices, each of which is AoE (WPB yards) in size, immediately moves randomly, inflicting +1 @Condition[Ablaze] Condition and a <em>magic missile</em> hit with Damage +4 and against all targets in their path. Smaller vortices disperse after moving once.</p><p><strong>Lore:</strong> You may inflict +1 @Condition[Ablaze] Condition on anyone targeted by spells from the Lore of Fire, unless they also possess the Arcane Magic (Fire) Talent. Every Ablaze condition within Willpower Bonus yards adds +10 to attempts to Channel or Cast with Aqshy.</p><p></p>"
    },
